N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 3 ยง 50.3 - Subpoena

State Regulations

The power of subpoena, set forth in Banking Law, section
38, shall extend to all matters relating to the affairs of any mutual trust
investment company. Notes
